{"tid":1772190,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"法國閪姐牛肉飯仲多人食過黃店，說好的懲罰呢？","createTime":"2019-12-06T11:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T09:32:39.000Z","uid":40386,"like":249,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"a30b3e0bf7a1efd5b2ee1e0721987847fef35efe","tid":1772190,"uid":40386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"星期五7點 岩岩目測閪姐牛肉飯做左5張單，旁邊拉面黃店都未有生意。<br />\n<br />\n公平咩？人地閪姐同哂光頭警長拍哂膊頭又成間鋪貼滿支那寶 大眾點評，差在未掛埋支那旗都好生意過你黃屍暴徒鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DsNgnAU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDsNgnAU.png&h=ccb4ed16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b22oM2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb22oM2N.png&h=4e1fd1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉個彎既水門雞飯就爆哂場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJA2h8V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJA2h8V.png&h=f7e744af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家唔好食水門雞飯，但一盒雞飯邊夠食呀<br />\n<br />\n人地拉面鋪有賣小食架  $30 鹽酥雞都好撚澎湃<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssFNuht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssFNuht.jpg&h=402fe0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想見到冇咁出名既黃店汁下又一間，汁下又一間，大家努力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"de4d563dd440956b2742c97077c7b56e22a0964b","tid":1772190,"uid":30251,"like":7,"dislike":87,"score":-80,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"$30 咁樣都幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申窮撚"},{"pid":"051ee56b0dfbe67ed2f26c07215055707b9db711","tid":1772190,"uid":64159,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"de4d563dd4